T1  - An Algorithm for the Solution of Mixed Integer Programming Problems
AU  - Driebeek, Norman J.
Y1  - 1966/03/01
PY  - 1966
DA  - 1966/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.12.7.576
